data.description: Start living the good life in this meticulously kept one-story home featuring three beds and two full baths. Loaded with upgrades, including the expanded primary suite that features a large bay window, custom mud set walk in shower and spacious closet, this home is a delight! Additional features to love include: extended tile into one bedroom, beautiful plantation style shutters and a large durable tuff shed for added backyard storage. The open floor plan allows you to stay connected as the party flows from the living area and onto the massive covered and tiled back patio perfect for grilling and enjoying the cooler Fall weather. The beautiful kitchen features, granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances with gas cooking! Added space between you and the neighbor and a fully-fenced yard provides extra privacy! Like-new one-story homes that offer this much to love typically sell quickly, so you are encouraged to set your showing today! [Grass has been digitally enhanced]
